                        m(b.categoryIds, b.vsCatIds) ||
                        q(a)
                            ? f('class', c)
                            : ((c = B(b.categoryIds, c, b.vsCatIds)),
                              f('class', c));
                        return !0;
                    }
                }
            }),
            (a.setAttribute = function (c, b, e) {
                ('type' !== c && 'src' !== c) || e ? f(c, b) : (a[c] = b);
            }),
            a
        );
    };
}()</script>
